# Project Overview

This is a monorepo managed with pnpm workspaces. The main configuration files are:

- [package.json](mdc:package.json) - Root package configuration
- [pnpm-workspace.yaml](mdc:pnpm-workspace.yaml) - Workspace configuration
- [turbo.json](mdc:turbo.json) - Turborepo configuration

## Directory Structure

- `apps/` - Contains application projects
  - `storybook/` - Storybook documentation app
- `libraries/` - Additional shared libraries
- `react/` - ReactJS specific libraries
- `tools/` - Development and build tools

## Development Setup

The project uses several tools for code quality:
- [.prettierrc.js](mdc:.prettierrc.js) - Prettier configuration
- [biome.jsonc](mdc:biome.jsonc) - Biome configuration
- [eslint.config.mjs](mdc:eslint.config.mjs) - ESLint configuration

For more information about contributing, see [CONTRIBUTING.md](mdc:CONTRIBUTING.md).
